data.description:
WATERFRONT PROPERTY located right on a canal that has DIRECT ACCESS to the WITHLACOOCHEE RIVER!! The boat house gives your boat protection from the weather & makes living on the river a breeze! Catch fish for dinner right off the dock! 
Like to see wildlife?... Numerous birds nest on the island across from the property. Turtles travel through the yard down to the bank. Imagine having the front row seat to this microcosm from your fully fenced yard. This home is so much bigger than it appears from the street. The OPEN FLOOR PLAN is just amazing!  The flow from the open kitchen to the living/dining combo & sunken family room allows for easy socializing for all. The POTBELLY electric fireplace with its brick hearth and beamed ceiling above provides a warm, inviting atmosphere for enjoying family gatherings. The flex space off the primary bedroom can be considered a dressing area/closet or office. The bonus room between the living room and back lanai features a full wall of closets making its functionality very versatile. Storage galore IN & OUT w/ an ample number of closets throughout. Under the house is partial storage, as well as 2 SHEDS and 2 CARPORTS, a double and a single, totaling three spaces. This property has so much to offer & so many different ways to enjoy it. Come on over & see what it's like by the River!
